  "term": "prop:bounds-sum-set",
  "kind": "Proposition",
  "title": "Bounds for Suprema and Infima Under Set Addition",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $A,B\\subseteq\\mathbb{R}$ be nonempty and bounded. Then\n\\[\n \\inf A+\\inf B\\le \\inf(A+B)\n \\qquad\\text{and}\\qquad\n \\sup(A+B)\\le \\sup A+\\sup B.\n\\]",
